name: CoreAPI Security_Group
description: API to access results security groups.
about:
Description

The CoreAPI Security_Group API enables to access security groups that are defined in the Security Group tool.

With this API, you can list all existing groups within the system, fetch all information regarding a specific groups, delete a group and, create groups.

Prerequisites: In order for the API to work, you will have to change the endpoint in the General tab.

Operations  performed

Important note: Please review the definitions and the request/response bodies for each operation.

/List

Get the list of available groups. Within each object in the returned array, the UUID of each item is placed. This is the same value that /Get operation requires.
